dct_title_s: Map of Persia, Turkey in Asia, Afghanistan, Beloochistan
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Bar scale on map given in "Miles".
Shows topography, drainage, boundaries, travel routes, places of historical interest.
"Entered according to act of Congress in the year 1860, by S. Augustus Mitchell, Jr., in the Clerk's Office of the District Court of the Eastern District of Pensylvania."
Inset map: Palestine of the Holy Land.
